full_summary:
================
### Geospatial Standards Development and Use for Arctic Land-Marine Information Interoperability

### Reference Number
PW-23-01020937

### Solicitation Number
NRCan-5000069563

### Publication Date
2023-01-11

### Tender Closing Date
2023-01-26T14:00:00

### Brief Description
Natural Resources Canada (NRCan) is seeking a contractor to develop and apply geospatial standards for the interoperability of terrestrial and marine land-marine information in the Arctic.

### Relevant Goods or Services
The contractor will be required to provide cartography services (T006A), marine cartography services (T007A), and mapping services for non-enumerated services (T016B).

### Trade Agreements
The tender is subject to the following trade agreements:

* Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA)
* Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA)
* Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)
* Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement 
* Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement
* Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
* Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP)
* Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-Ukraine Free Trade Agreement (CUFTA)
* World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO GPA)
* Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA)
* Canada-UK Trade Continuity Agreement (Canada-UK TCA)

### Contact Information
For more information, please contact Catherine Boilard at NRCan:

Email: [catherine.boilard@rncan-nrcan.gc.ca](mailto:catherine.boilard@rncan-nrcan.gc.ca)
Phone: 418-254-4882

### Tender Documents
The tender documents for this opportunity can be found on Buyandsell.gc.ca:

https://canadabuys.canada.ca/documents/pub/att/2023/01/11/ab1ceeae43f3df5dd4505ae9f38a7bdf/acan_nrcan-5000069563_-_173586.pdf

### Expiry Date
The tender closing date was January 26, 2023.  Please note that the tender status is expired. 

### Expected Contract Start and End Dates
The expected contract start and end dates have not been specified in the provided information.
